{"title":"深层[无意识的基因]","time_limit":2000,"memory_limit":512,"tags":["2020小学期","数论","分类讨论"],"operation":{"submit":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1198#submit_code","submissions":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/submissions?problem_id=1198","statistics":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1198/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1198/testdata","discussion":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/discussion/problem/1198"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"已知两个正整数 $n,s$，求一个最小的正整数 $b$，使得如果将 $n$ 写成 $b$ 进制，那么 $n$ 的各位数字之和为 $s$,形式化地说，即 $n=\\displaystyle\\sum_{i=0}^{\\infty}n_ib^i,(0\\leq n_i<b ),\\sum_{i=0}^{\\infty}n_i=s$。输出最小的 $b$，若不存在，输出 $-1$\r\n\r\n注意，$b$ 不可能是 $1$，因为1进制只能表示 $0$."},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"第一行一个正整数 $n$.\r\n\r\n第二行一个正整数 $s$."},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"一行一个整数表示答案."},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"#### 样例输入1\r\n```plain\r\n87654\r\n30\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输出1\r\n```plain\r\n10\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输入2\r\n```plain\r\n87654\r\n138\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输出2\r\n```plain\r\n100\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输入3\r\n```plain\r\n87654\r\n45678\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输出3\r\n```plain\r\n-1\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输入4\r\n```plain\r\n31415926535\r\n1\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输出4\r\n```plain\r\n31415926535\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输入5\r\n```plain\r\n1\r\n31415926535\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输出5\r\n```plain\r\n-1\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"$1\\leq n,s\\leq 10^{11}$"}]}